Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:39.41,SongOP,ko,0,0,0,,싸우는 한껏 고요함과 함께
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:39.41,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Fight the utmost with the stillness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:45.67,SongOP,ko,0,0,0,,무예! 이도류 무사시
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:45.67,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Martial Arts! Dual Blade Musashi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.67,0:01:50.88,SongOP,ko,0,0,0,,미간이 반짝였다 무사시!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.67,0:01:50.88,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,His eyes shined! Musashi!
Comment: 0,0:02:00.19,0:02:04.67,Default,ja,0,0,0,,不知火の浜にはまった武蔵は独のためにしびれてしまった。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.19,0:02:04.67,Default,ko,0,0,0,,시라누이의 함정에 빠진 무사시는 독 때문에 마비되고 말았다.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.19,0:02:04.67,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi fell into Shiranui's trap, and was paralyzed by poison.
Comment: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:10.01,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そしてコジローは愛刀、物干竿を折られ、失意のどん底に。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:10.01,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그리고 코지로는 애도 모노호시자오가 부러져, 실의의 밑바닥으로.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:10.01,Default,en,0,0,0,,And Kojirō got his beloved sword Monohoshizao broken, and fell into the very bottom of despair.
Comment: 0,0:02:10.79,0:02:14.15,Default,ja,0,0,0,,何とか立ち直らせろうとする武蔵、千姫であったが、
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.79,0:02:14.15,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어떻게든 재기시켜 주려는 무사시와 센히메였지만.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.79,0:02:14.15,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi and Senhime were trying to recover Kojirō,
Comment: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:17.60,Default,ja,0,0,0,,えへ、うまくはいかなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:17.60,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어허, 잘 안 되고 있었다.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:17.60,Default,en,0,0,0,,why, it wasn't working out so well.
Comment: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:22.98,TitleEP,ja,0,0,0,,今よみがえる伝説の剣だす
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:22.98,TitleEP,ko,0,0,190,,지금 되살아나는
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:22.98,TitleEP,ko,0,0,50,,전설의 검이오
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:22.98,TitleEP,en,0,0,190,,The Reviving
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:22.98,TitleEP,en,0,0,50,,Legendary Sword
Comment: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:42.47,Default,ja,0,0,0,,愛刀、物干竿を壊らされてしまったコジローは、まるで魂が抜けたようにおっと、しっぱなしであった。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:42.47,Default,ko,0,0,0,,애도 모노호시자오가 부서진 코지로는 마치 혼이 빠져나간 듯 계속 실연에 빠져 있었다.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:42.47,Default,en,0,0,0,,After having his beloved sword Monohashizao broken, Kojirō was deep in despair, as if his spirit was lost.
Comment: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:48.34,Default,ja,0,0,0,,コジロー？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:48.34,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코지로?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:48.34,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojirō?
Comment: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:53.55,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいら、いくだす！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:53.55,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나, 가오!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:53.55,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will go-{\i1}dasu{\i0} !
Comment: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:55.66,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いくって、どこへ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:55.66,Default,ko,0,0,0,,간다니 어디에?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:55.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,Go to where?
Comment: 0,0:02:56.06,0:02:58.63,Default,ja,0,0,0,,決まってるんだす！天草島へ行くんだす！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:02:58.63,Default,ko,0,0,0,,당연한 것이오! 아마쿠사도에 가오!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:02:58.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's obvious-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I'm going to Amakusa Island-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:02.53,Default,ja,0,0,0,,不知火一族に殺されに行くようなもんでごわすぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:02.53,Default,ko,0,0,0,,시라누이 일족에게 죽으러 가는 것과 마찬가지요.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:02.53,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's just like going there just to be killed by Shiranul Clan-{\i1}gowasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:11.65,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そんなこと言ってたら何もできないだす！だって、おいら、あんなコジローの姿見てられないだす。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:11.65,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그런 생각을 하면 아무것도 못 하오! 무엇보다도, 나, 저런 코지로를 보고만 있을 수는 없소.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:11.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,With that kind of way of thinking, you can't do anything-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! Most of all, I can't stand seeing Kojirō like that-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:22.36,Default,ja,0,0,0,,武蔵。お前がドジでクマソンの罠にはまるからこういうことになったのだ。私は嫌だったんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:22.36,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시. 네가 바보라서 쿠마손의 함정에 빠져서 이렇게 된 것이다. 난 싫었다.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:22.36,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi. This all happened because you're foolish enough to be fallen into Kumason's trap. I did not wanted to join.
Comment: 0,0:03:23.99,0:03:26.91,Default,ja,0,0,0,,武蔵が悪いんだ。武蔵が。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.99,0:03:26.91,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시 잘못이다. 무사시 잘못.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.99,0:03:26.91,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's all Musashi's fault. Musashi was wrong.
Comment: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:29.05,Default,ja,0,0,0,,再起不能でゴワスか。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:29.05,Default,ko,0,0,0,,재기 불능인가.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:29.05,Default,en,0,0,0,,Is he not recoverable-{\i1}gowasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:34.03,Default,ja,0,0,0,,彩って、いつまでもおいらのことせめてつもりだすよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:34.03,Default,ko,0,0,0,,사과해도 언제까지나 날 원망할 생각이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:34.03,Default,en,0,0,0,,Even if I apologize, he'll going to blame me forever-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:38.94,Default,ja,0,0,0,,物干竿は本当に自分の分身みたいなものだったからね。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:38.94,Default,ko,0,0,0,,모노호시자오는 정말로 자신의 분신 같은 것이었으니 말이야.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:38.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,Monohoshizao was truly like his other self.
Comment: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:45.85,Default,ja,0,0,0,,だから責任を取って、おいらが物干竿に代わる秘剣を、天草島に行って探してくるダス！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:45.85,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그러니까 책임을 지고 내가 모노호시자오에 견줄 비검을 아마쿠사도에 찾으러 가오!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:45.85,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's why I'm going to be responsible and go to Amakusa Island to find that secret sword on a par with Monohoshizao!
Comment: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:49.18,Default,ja,0,0,0,,待って、武蔵。気持ちはわかるけど、危険よ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:49.18,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잠깐, 무사시. 마음은 알겠는데 위험해.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:49.18,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wait, Musashi. I understand you, but it's too dangerous.
Comment: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:55.63,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あ、おいらはいかなきゃいけないんだす！止めてくれるな、おせんちゃん！その手を放してくれだす！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:55.63,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 나는 가야만 하오. 막지 마시오, 센짱! 그 손을 놓으시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:55.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,Oh, but I must go-{\i1}dasu{\i0}. Do not stop me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! Unhand me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:59.29,Default,ja,0,0,0,,放せ！放せ！放せダス！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:59.29,Default,ko,0,0,0,,놓아! 놓아! 놓으시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:59.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,Unhand me! Unhand me! Let me go-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:01.11,Default,ja,0,0,0,,初めからつかんでいないわよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:01.11,Default,ko,0,0,0,,애초에 안 잡았어.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:01.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,I didn't hold you at the first place.
Comment: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:06.28,Default,ja,0,0,0,,バカ目。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:06.28,Default,ko,0,0,0,,바보 자식.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:06.28,Default,en,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Comment: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:11.76,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あら？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:11.76,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어라?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:11.76,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:17.11,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ちょうどいいダス。この船、お借りするダス！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:17.11,Default,ko,0,0,0,,마침 딱 잘 됐소. 이 배 빌리겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:17.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,This is just right-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I'll borrow this ship-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:18.93,Default,ja,0,0,0,,武蔵！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:18.93,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:18.93,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi!
Comment: 0,0:04:21.08,0:04:23.10,Default,ja,0,0,0,,みんな武蔵が悪いんですよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.08,0:04:23.10,Default,ko,0,0,0,,모든 건 무사시 잘못입니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.08,0:04:23.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,Everything is Musashi's fault.
Comment: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:36.79,Default,ja,0,0,0,,うるさいだすな。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:36.79,Default,ko,0,0,0,,시끄럽소...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:36.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,How noisy-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:43.39,Default,ja,0,0,0,,武蔵。お前のせいだ。武蔵！武蔵！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:43.39,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시. 네 잘못이다. 무사시! 무사시!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:43.39,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi! It's your fault. Musashi! Musashi!
Comment: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:47.60,Default,ja,0,0,0,,コジロー、許してくれだす。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:47.60,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코지로, 용서해 주시오...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:47.60,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojirō, please forgive me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:52.94,Default,ja,0,0,0,,夢だすか。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:52.94,Default,ko,0,0,0,,꿈이었소...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:52.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,It was just a dream-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:26.77,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いって！痛いダス！うわ！助けてくれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:26.77,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아야! 아프오! 으악! 살려주시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:26.77,Default,en,0,0,0,,Ouch! That hurts-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! Waaah! Help me!
Comment: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:31.73,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いっていだす。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:31.73,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아팠소...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:31.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,That hurt...
Comment: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:37.79,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ここが天草島ダスか！話雰囲気はどこにもないダスが。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:37.79,Default,ko,0,0,0,,여기가 아마쿠사 섬이오. 수상한 분위기는 어디에도 없소...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:37.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,This must be that Amakusa Island-{\i1}dasu{\i0}. I don't feel anything suspicious-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:45.00,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そういえば夕べから何も食べてなかった出す。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:45.00,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그러고 보니 어젯밤부터 아무것도 안 먹었소.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:45.00,Default,en,0,0,0,,I just remembered that I didn't eat anything since last night-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:50.13,Default,ja,0,0,0,,すいませんだす！この辺にお団子やさんないダスか！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:50.13,Default,ko,0,0,0,,실례하오! 이 주변에 단고집 있소?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:50.13,Default,en,0,0,0,,Excuse me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! Is there a dango house around here-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:54.16,Default,ja,0,0,0,,もしもしだす！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:54.16,Default,ko,0,0,0,,누구 있소?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:54.16,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hello-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:56.50,Default,ja,0,0,0,,留守から。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:56.50,Default,ko,0,0,0,,외출이오...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:56.50,Default,en,0,0,0,,Absent, I guess...
Comment: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:03.46,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ごめんくださいダス！この辺にお団子やさんないんだすか！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:03.46,Default,ko,0,0,0,,실례하오! 이 주변에 단고집 있소?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:03.46,Default,en,0,0,0,,Excuse me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! Is there a dango house around here-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:06.45,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいら、おなか減って、死にそうなんだす。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:06.45,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나, 배고파서 죽을 것 같소.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:06.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'm gonna die of hunger-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:09.19,Default,ja,0,0,0,,誰かいるダスか！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:09.19,Default,ko,0,0,0,,누구 있소?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:09.19,Default,en,0,0,0,,Is anyone there-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!
Comment: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:11.36,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ちょっと待ってくれだす！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:11.36,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잠깐 기다리시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:11.36,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wait for me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:13.84,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ど、どこいっただす。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:13.84,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어, 어디 갔소...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:13.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,W- where did they go-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:17.77,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あ、腹減って動けないだす。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:17.77,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 배고파서 못 움직이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:17.77,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'm too hungry to move-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:06:21.89,0:06:23.05,Default,ja,0,0,0,,誰かいるダスか！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.89,0:06:23.05,Default,ko,0,0,0,,누구 있소?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.89,0:06:23.05,Default,en,0,0,0,,Anybody there-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!
Comment: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:26.72,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいら、何でもいいから食べたいんだす、ね！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:26.72,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나, 아무거나 좋으니까 먹고 싶소! 꼭!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:26.72,Default,en,0,0,0,,I want to eat anything possible-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! Please!
Comment: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:28.93,Default,ja,0,0,0,,誰だす！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:28.93,Default,ko,0,0,0,,누구이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:28.93,Default,en,0,0,0,,Who's there-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!
Comment: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:39.30,Default,ja,0,0,0,,?????????????? かちだったダス。おいら、敵に囲まれしまった出す！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:39.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,함정인 것 같소. 나, 적에게 둘러싸였소!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:39.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,It looks like a trap-{\i1}dasu{\i0}. I'm surrounded by enemies-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:43.59,Default,ja,0,0,0,,やめるダス！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:43.59,Default,ko,0,0,0,,관두시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:43.59,Default,en,0,0,0,,Stop it-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:45.41,Default,ja,0,0,0,,父ちゃん、母ちゃん、返せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:45.41,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아빠 엄마 돌려줘!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:45.41,Default,en,0,0,0,,Give my daddy and mommy back!
Comment: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:47.71,Default,ja,0,0,0,,不知火一族なんかやっつけてやる！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:47.71,Default,ko,0,0,0,,시라누이 일족 따위 해치워버릴 거야!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:47.71,Default,en,0,0,0,,We'll get rid of any Shiranui Clan!
Comment: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:57.34,Default,ja,0,0,0,,待つだす！人違いだすよ！おいら、不知火一族やっつけるためにここに来たダス！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:57.34,Default,ko,0,0,0,,멈추시오! 사람 잘못 봤소! 나, 시라누이 일족을 해치우기 위해 여기에 왔소!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:57.34,Default,en,0,0,0,,Stop-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! You've got it wrong-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I'm here to take care of Shiranui Clan-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:00.43,Default,ja,0,0,0,,へ？みんな攻撃やめろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:00.43,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어? 다들 공격 멈춰!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:00.43,Default,en,0,0,0,,What? Everyone, stop attacking!
Comment: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:01.34,Default,ja,0,0,0,,はい！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:01.34,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:01.34,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Comment: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:03.97,Default,ja,0,0,0,,名前を聞けばわかるだす。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:03.97,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이름을 들으면 아오!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:03.97,Default,en,0,0,0,,You'll know it when you hear my name-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:10.18,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいら、ジパングナンバーワンのからくり武芸者を目指す、宮本村の武蔵でござるだす。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:10.18,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나, 지팡구 제일의 카라쿠리 무예가가 되고자 하는 미야모토 마을의 무사시이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:10.18,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am the number one Karakuri martial artist of future of Jipangu, Musashi from Miyamoto village-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:11.85,Default,ja,0,0,0,,知らないだす！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:11.85,Default,ko,0,0,0,,모르오!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:11.85,Default,en,0,0,0,,Never heard of him-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:17.35,Default,ja,0,0,0,,だけど、よく見るとこの間村を襲ってきたやつらとは違うな。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:17.35,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그래도, 잘 보면 요새 마을에 덤벼든 놈들하고는 다르네.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:17.35,Default,en,0,0,0,,But anyway, he does look different from the ones who came to attack the village!
Comment: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:23.47,Default,ja,0,0,0,,うん。あいつらはみんな目つきが悪かったけど、この兄ちゃんはすんだいいめをしてるぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:23.47,Default,ko,0,0,0,,응. 놈들은 다들 눈매가 나빴는데, 이 형은 좋은 눈매야.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:23.47,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yeah. They looked like they had ill will, but this brother has a good look!
Comment: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:28.12,Default,ja,0,0,0,,君たち、きっと見る目があるね！なんか～だす！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:28.12,Default,ko,0,0,0,,너희들 사람 보는 눈이 있소! 왠지 해 드려야겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:28.12,Default,en,0,0,0,,You guys do have a discerning eye-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I must do something for you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:29.06,Default,ja,0,0,0,,本当？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:29.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,정말?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:29.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,Really?!
Comment: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:33.15,Default,ja,0,0,0,,でも、その前になんか食わせてくれダス。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:33.15,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그래도 그 전에 뭔가 먹게 해 주시오.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:33.15,Default,en,0,0,0,,But before that, let me eat something-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:07:39.67,0:07:40.63,Default,ja,0,0,0,,うまいうまいうまい！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.67,0:07:40.63,Default,ko,0,0,0,,맛있소맛있소맛있소!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.67,0:07:40.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's so good!
Comment: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:43.30,Default,ja,0,0,0,,?????? なげもうまい。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:43.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,싹도 맛있소.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:43.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,Even the leaf is good-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:48.65,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あ、俺たちもよく食うけど、武蔵の兄貴みたいに食べる人は初めて見たな。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:48.65,Default,ko,0,0,0,,우리도 잘 먹긴 하는데, 무사시 형처럼 먹는 사람은 처음 봐.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:48.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,We eat much, but I never saw someone who eat as much as Musashi bro!
Comment: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:52.12,Default,ja,0,0,0,,本当。もう20本目よ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:52.12,Default,ko,0,0,0,,정말. 벌써 20개 째야.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:52.12,Default,en,0,0,0,,Really. He already ate 20!
Comment: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:58.05,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あ、そうだ。この島に伝説の秘剣があるだすか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:58.05,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 그렇소. 이 섬에 전설의 비검이 있소?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:58.05,Default,en,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Is there any legendary secret sword in this island-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:01.71,Default,ja,0,0,0,,伝説の秘剣？そりゃ、鳳凰丸のことだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:01.71,Default,ko,0,0,0,,전설의 비검? 그거, 봉황환 말이야?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:01.71,Default,en,0,0,0,,By that legendary secret sword, do you mean Hououmaru?
Comment: 0,0:08:02.47,0:08:05.30,Default,ja,0,0,0,,鳳凰丸っていうだすか！どこにあるだす？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.47,0:08:05.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,봉황환이었소! 어디 있소?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.47,0:08:05.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,So that was Hououmaru! Where is it?
Comment: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:10.75,Default,ja,0,0,0,,うちの父ちゃんが大事に持ってたんだけど、不知火一族がもってっちゃったんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:10.75,Default,ko,0,0,0,,우리 아빠가 소중하게 관리하고 있었는데 시라누이 일족이 가져갔어.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:10.75,Default,en,0,0,0,,My dad was taking care of it preciously, but then Shiranui Clan took it.
Comment: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:14.06,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なんだって？！・一か月ほど前のある夜。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:14.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,-뭣이오?!\N-한 달 정도 전에.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:14.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,-What-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!\N-About a month ago.
Comment: 0,0:08:21.05,0:08:29.99,Default,ja,0,0,0,,不知火一族が現れ、島中の人たちを連れ去って、おまけに刀、鍬、犂なんかもすべて奪っていってしまったんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.05,0:08:29.99,Default,ko,0,0,0,,시라누이 일족이 나타나 섬에 있는 모든 사람을 데려가고, 게다가 칼, 괭이, 쟁기 따위를 죄다 빼앗아가 버렸어.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.05,0:08:29.99,Default,en,0,0,0,,Shiranui Clan has appeared to take all the people on the island, and in addition, they took all the swords, hoes, and spades.
Comment: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:36.40,Default,ja,0,0,0,,その時、何とか逃げた俺たちだけが助かったんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:36.40,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그 때, 어떻게든 우린 도망쳐서 살았어.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:36.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,During that, we somehow escaped and we're here.
Comment: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:38.68,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そうだったんだすか。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:38.68,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그랬소.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:38.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,So that's what happened-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:43.41,Default,ja,0,0,0,,不知火一族は、あたいの母ちゃんどこに連れて行っちゃったんだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:43.41,Default,ko,0,0,0,,시라누이 일족은 우리 엄마를 어디로 데려갔을까...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:43.41,Default,en,0,0,0,,I wonder where did that Shiranui Clan take my mommy to...
Comment: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:48.36,Default,ja,0,0,0,,お父ちゃん！お母ちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:48.36,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아빠! 엄마!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:48.36,Default,en,0,0,0,,Daddy! Mommy!
Comment: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:05.46,NoteOnAnime,ja,0,0,53,,{\fad(360,0)}イカヅチ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:05.46,NoteOnAnime,ko,0,0,53,,{\fad(360,0)}이카즈치
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:05.46,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,53,,{\fad(360,0)}Ikazuchi
Comment: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:24.92,Default,ja,0,0,0,,俺様は不知火一族のイカヅチだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:24.92,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나는 시라누이 일족의 이카즈치다.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:24.92,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am one of Shiranui Clan, Ikazuchi!
Comment: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:29.32,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいらはジパングナンバーワンの武芸者を目指す、武蔵でござるだす。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:29.32,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나는 지팡구 제일의 무예가가 될 무사시이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:29.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am Musashi, the future number one martial artist of Jipangu!
Comment: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:30.61,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あら？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:30.61,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어라?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:30.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:36.83,Default,ja,0,0,0,,武蔵。飛んで火にいる夏の虫とは、貴様のことだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:36.83,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시. 날아 불에 들어오는 여름의 벌레는 네놈을 말하는구나!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:36.83,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi. You are here to rush to your doom!
Comment: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:40.57,Default,ja,0,0,0,,うるさいダス！村の人たちはどこへやったダスか！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:40.57,Default,ko,0,0,0,,시끄럽소! 마을 사람들을 어디에 데려갔소!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:40.57,Default,en,0,0,0,,Shut up-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! Where did you take the villagers-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!
Comment: 0,0:09:40.57,0:09:41.77,Default,ja,0,0,0,,知りたいか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.57,0:09:41.77,Default,ko,0,0,0,,알고 싶냐?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.57,0:09:41.77,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wanna know?
Comment: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:42.76,Default,ja,0,0,0,,当たり前だす！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:42.76,Default,ko,0,0,0,,당연하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:42.76,Default,en,0,0,0,,Of course-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:46.88,Default,ja,0,0,0,,返しはしないがどこにいるか見せてやろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:46.88,Default,ko,0,0,0,,돌려 주진 않을 테지만 어디 있는지는 보여 주지.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:46.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,I won't free them, but I'll let you know where they are.
Comment: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:49.29,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいらが戦ってる間に逃げるダス。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:49.29,Default,ko,0,0,0,,내가 싸울 동안 도망치시오.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:49.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,Run away while I fight-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:52.59,Default,ja,0,0,0,,わかった。兄ちゃん一人で大丈夫か？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:52.59,Default,ko,0,0,0,,알았어. 형 혼자 괜찮아?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:52.59,Default,en,0,0,0,,Got it. Are you really okay by yourself?
Comment: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:54.10,Default,ja,0,0,0,,当たり前だす！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:54.10,Default,ko,0,0,0,,당연하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:54.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,Of course-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:09:54.21,0:09:56.56,Default,ja,0,0,0,,イカヅチ弾を見舞いしてやる！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.21,0:09:56.56,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이카즈치 탄을 보여 주겠다!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.21,0:09:56.56,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'll show you Ikazuchi Shell!
Comment: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:15.52,Default,ja,0,0,0,,点が呼んだか地が招いたか、この世の悪を退治する男武蔵！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:15.52,Default,ko,0,0,0,,하늘이 부르고 땅이 불렀소! 이 세상의 악을 퇴치할 사내 무사시!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:15.52,Default,en,0,0,0,,The sky called and the ground called Musashi, the man who will take care of all the evil in this world!
Comment: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:17.30,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ただいま惨状だす。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:17.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,지금 등장하오.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:17.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'm here to fight-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:25.74,Default,ja,0,0,0,,二天一流！鉄風車！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:25.74,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이천일류 철풍차!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:25.74,Default,en,0,0,0,,Nitenichiryu: Iron Windmill!
Comment: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:37.31,Default,ja,0,0,0,,うん？しょことないなことを！イカヅチ弾を見舞いしてやる！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:37.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,음? 건방진 꼬맹이가! 이카즈치 탄을 맛보아라!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:37.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,Aren't you an impudent brat?! Take my Ikazuchi Shell!
Comment: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:44.48,Default,ja,0,0,0,,覚悟！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:44.48,Default,ko,0,0,0,,각오해라!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:44.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself!
Comment: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:12.04,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ここは不知火一族の秘密工場だすな。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:12.04,Default,ko,0,0,0,,여긴 시라누이 일족의 비밀 공장이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:12.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,This must be the secret factory of Shiranui Clan.
Comment: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:14.82,Default,ja,0,0,0,,くそ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:14.82,Default,ko,0,0,0,,젠장!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:14.82,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn!
Comment: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:22.10,Default,ja,0,0,0,,約束通り見つけてやったぞ。島の地下にいる村人たちを。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:22.10,Default,ko,0,0,0,,약속대로 보여줬다. 섬 지하에 있는 마을 사람들을!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:22.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,I showed them as promised. The villagers are in underground of the island!
Comment: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:25.86,Default,ja,0,0,0,,こんなところで働かせて！いったい何を企んでるだす！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:25.86,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이런 곳에서 일이나 시키고 대체 뭘 꾸미고 있소!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:25.86,Default,en,0,0,0,,Why would you make them work in a place like this-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!
Comment: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:27.29,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あれを見ろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:27.29,Default,ko,0,0,0,,저걸 봐라!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:27.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,Take a look at that!
Comment: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:31.19,Default,ja,0,0,0,,新式の大砲、鉄砲を作っているのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:31.19,Default,ko,0,0,0,,신식 대포, 철포를 만들고 있다.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:31.19,Default,en,0,0,0,,We are making new type cannons and guns.
Comment: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:33.24,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あ？あんなにたくさん？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:33.24,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어? 저렇게 잔뜩?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:33.24,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh? That many?
Comment: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:38.78,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あれだけあれば、エドトピアを全滅させることなど朝飯米。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:38.78,Default,ko,0,0,0,,저만큼 있으면 에도토피아를 전멸하는 것도 아주 쉽다!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:38.78,Default,en,0,0,0,,With that many, it is trivial to annihilate Edotopia!
Comment: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:43.09,Default,ja,0,0,0,,すなわち、天河は我々不知火一族のものなのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:43.09,Default,ko,0,0,0,,즉, 천하는 우리 시라누이 일족의 것이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:43.09,Default,en,0,0,0,,Meaning that the world is under Shiranui Clan's hands!
Comment: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:48.76,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そんなにうまくいってたまるだすか！このおいらがそんなことはさせないだす！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:48.76,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그렇게 되도록 냅둘 것 같소이까! 이 내가 그렇게 하도록 안 두오!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:48.76,Default,en,0,0,0,,I won't let that happen-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I'll stop you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:54.09,Default,ja,0,0,0,,しかし、武蔵よ、いくら息があっても死んでは何もできない。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:54.09,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그렇지만 무사시, 아무리 의지가 있어도 죽으면 아무것도 못 한다.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:54.09,Default,en,0,0,0,,But Musashi, you can't do anything if you die, no matter how deeply you desire.
Comment: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:55.23,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なに？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:55.23,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭣이오?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:55.23,Default,en,0,0,0,,What?!
Comment: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:04.62,Default,ja,0,0,0,,これはできたばかりの鉄砲だ。この威力をお前を打つことによって試してやる。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:04.62,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이건 막 만들어진 철포다. 이 위력을 네게 쏘아 시험해 주마!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:04.62,Default,en,0,0,0,,This gun was just made. I will test its might by shooting this to you!
Comment: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:08.11,Default,ja,0,0,0,,わ！そんなこと貯めさなくだっていいだす！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:08.11,Default,ko,0,0,0,,으악! 그런 건 시험해 보지 않아도 괜찮소!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:08.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wah! You don't have to test that to find it out!
Comment: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:10.04,Default,ja,0,0,0,,覚悟がいいな！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:10.04,Default,ko,0,0,0,,각오해라!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:10.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hope you're prepared!
Comment: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:11.76,Default,ja,0,0,0,,しない！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:11.76,Default,ko,0,0,0,,안 하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:11.76,Default,en,0,0,0,,I won't!
Comment: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:18.53,Default,ja,0,0,0,,とうとう命を落としのか、武蔵！疾風怒濤のご飯を待って！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:18.53,Default,ko,0,0,0,,결국 목숨을 잃는가, 무사시! 질풍노도의 후반을 기다려라!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:18.53,Default,en,0,0,0,,Will Musashi finally lose his life?! Wait for the stormy latter half!
Comment: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:23.49,Eyecatch,ja,0,0,0,,EC
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:23.49,Eyecatch,ko,0,0,0,,카라쿠리 검호전 무사시 로드
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:23.49,Eyecatch,en,0,0,0,,Karakuri Kengouden: Musashi Road
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:23.49,Eyecatch,,0,0,0,,{\an2}by Subdivers
Comment: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:31.94,Default,ja,0,0,0,,やられた！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:31.94,Default,ko,0,0,0,,당했소!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:31.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,I got hit!
Comment: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:36.10,Default,ja,0,0,0,,うん？弾を入れてなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:36.10,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어? 총알을 넣지 않았군.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:36.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hm? I didn't charge it with ammo.
Comment: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:41.17,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なんだすって？！せっかく覚悟してたのに！さっさと打つだす！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:41.17,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭣이오?! 기껏 각오했더니! 어서 쏘시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:41.17,Default,en,0,0,0,,What did you say-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?! I tried hard to prepare-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! Hurry up and shoot-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:44.68,Default,ja,0,0,0,,心配するな！今すぐあの世へ送ってやる！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:44.68,Default,ko,0,0,0,,걱정 마라! 지금 곧 저 세상에 보내 주마!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:44.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't worry! You're going to hell soon!
Comment: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:49.34,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いいか！今度こそ行くぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:49.34,Default,ko,0,0,0,,알겠냐! 이번에야말로 간다!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:49.34,Default,en,0,0,0,,Understand this! You're going this time!
Comment: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:54.64,Default,ja,0,0,0,,誰だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:54.64,Default,ko,0,0,0,,누구냐!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:54.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,Who's that?!
Comment: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:00.28,Default,ja,0,0,0,,うん？貴様は！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:00.28,Default,ko,0,0,0,,음? 네놈은!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:00.28,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hm? You bastard!
Comment: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:21.08,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ジュウベエさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:21.08,Default,ko,0,0,0,,쥬베 씨!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:21.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,Mr. Jube!
Comment: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:22.89,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なに？ジュウベエ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:22.89,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐? 쥬베?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:22.89,Default,en,0,0,0,,What? Jube?
Comment: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:27.38,Default,ja,0,0,0,,不知火一族の秘密の兵器工場、しかと見せてもらったぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:27.38,Default,ko,0,0,0,,시라누이 일족의 비밀 병기 공장. 단단히 봐 두었다!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:27.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,I've seen Shiranui Clan's secret weapon factory for sure!
Comment: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:34.61,Default,ja,0,0,0,,イエヤスの犬目！いつの間に忍び込みよって！だがお前の命もここまでだと知れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:34.61,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이에야스의 개자식! 어느새 몰래 들어왔나! 그렇지만 네 명줄도 여기까지인 줄 알아라!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:34.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,Ieyasu's underling! How did you sneak in?! Anyway, know that your life ends now!
Comment: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:47.73,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ジュウベエさん、ありがとうだす！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:47.73,Default,ko,0,0,0,,쥬베 씨, 고맙소!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:47.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mr. Jube!
Comment: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:50.60,Default,ja,0,0,0,,己己！くらえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:50.60,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 자식이! 먹어라!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:50.60,Default,en,0,0,0,,How dare you, you bastard?! Take this!
Comment: 0,0:14:00.09,0:14:01.38,Default,ja,0,0,0,,覚悟しろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.09,0:14:01.38,Default,ko,0,0,0,,각오해라!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.09,0:14:01.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself!
Comment: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:03.93,Default,ja,0,0,0,,待て！私が相手をする！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:03.93,Default,ko,0,0,0,,멈춰라! 넌 내가 상대한다!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:03.93,Default,en,0,0,0,,Stop! I'll face you!
Comment: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:05.99,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ふん！望むところだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:05.99,Default,ko,0,0,0,,흥! 바라던 바라!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:05.99,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hmph! Just as I wanted!
Comment: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:12.15,Default,ja,0,0,0,,愚かなやつ。・なに？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:12.15,Default,ko,0,0,0,,-멍청한 자식.\N-뭐?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:12.15,Default,en,0,0,0,,-What a fool.\N-What?!
Comment: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:28.74,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいらもやるだす！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:28.74,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나도 하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:28.74,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'll fight too-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:35.99,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そこまでだ！武蔵！ジュウベエ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:35.99,Default,ko,0,0,0,,거기까지다! 무사시! 쥬베!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:35.99,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's as far as you go, Musashi, Jube!
Comment: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:43.72,Default,ja,0,0,0,,村人たちを殺されたくなかったあら刀を捨てろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:43.72,Default,ko,0,0,0,,마을 사람들을 죽이기 싫다면 칼을 내려두어라!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:43.72,Default,en,0,0,0,,If you don't want to kill the villagers, then put your sword down!
Comment: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:45.20,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ひ、秘境だす！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:45.20,Default,ko,0,0,0,,비, 비겁하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:45.20,Default,en,0,0,0,,H- how cowardly!
Comment: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:52.33,Default,ja,0,0,0,,戦いに秘境減ったくれもないわ。頭のいいものが勝つ！そういうことだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:52.33,Default,ko,0,0,0,,전투에 비겁하고 자시고 하는 거 없다! 머리 좋은 놈이 이길 뿐이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:52.33,Default,en,0,0,0,,There's no coward or whatsoever in a battle! Whoever is smarter wins, and that's it!
Comment: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:56.88,Default,ja,0,0,0,,やもうえん。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:56.88,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어쩔 수 없군.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:56.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,We have no choice.
Comment: 0,0:14:57.42,0:15:00.06,Default,ja,0,0,0,,刀を捨てる必要はないでゴワス！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:15:00.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,칼을 내려둘 필요는 없소!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:15:00.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,There is no need to put your swords down-{\i1}gowasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:06.83,Default,ja,0,0,0,,せんちゃん！サイゴーさん！コジロー！どうしてここへ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:06.83,Default,ko,0,0,0,,센짱! 사이고 씨! 코지로! 어째서 여기에!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:06.83,Default,en,0,0,0,,Sen-chan! Mr. Saigo! Kojirō! How did you get here?!
Comment: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:09.78,Default,ja,0,0,0,,武蔵一人では心配だからやってきたのよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:09.78,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시 혼자서는 걱정되니까 왔어!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:09.78,Default,en,0,0,0,,We were worried about you, Musashi, especially since you're alone!
Comment: 0,0:15:10.07,0:15:14.50,Default,ja,0,0,0,,さぁ、不知火君、おとなしく武器を捨ててもらおうでゴワス。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.07,0:15:14.50,Default,ko,0,0,0,,자, 시라누이 군, 순순히 무기를 내려두시오.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.07,0:15:14.50,Default,en,0,0,0,,Now, now, Shiranui, put your weapons down-{\i1}gowasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:21.34,Default,ja,0,0,0,,残念。そういいたいところだが、そっちこそ無駄なことはやめておけ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:21.34,Default,ko,0,0,0,,안됐군. 이라고 하고 싶던 참이지만 그쪽이야말로 헛짓은 관둬라.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:21.34,Default,en,0,0,0,,Too bad. You're the ones to give up with futile actions.
Comment: 0,0:15:21.93,0:15:23.68,Default,ja,0,0,0,,無駄なことでゴワスか。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.93,0:15:23.68,Default,ko,0,0,0,,헛짓이오?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.93,0:15:23.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,Futile actions-{\i1}gowasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:28.89,Default,ja,0,0,0,,その通り！その鉄砲にはまだ弾が入っていないのだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:28.89,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그렇다! 그 철포에는 아직 총알이 들어가 있지 않다!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:28.89,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's right! There's no ammo in those guns yet!
Comment: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:33.26,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なに？！参ったでゴワスな。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:33.26,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭣이?! 곤란하오...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:33.26,Default,en,0,0,0,,What did you say?! Well, that's bad-{\i1}gowasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:35.65,Default,ja,0,0,0,,みんな武蔵が悪いんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:35.65,Default,ko,0,0,0,,모두 무사시 탓이다.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:35.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's all Musashi's fault.
Comment: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:43.64,Default,ja,0,0,0,,サイゴー、コジロー、千姫もまとめてあの世へ送ってるとはめでたいことだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:43.64,Default,ko,0,0,0,,사이고, 코지로, 센히메도 한꺼번에 저 세상에 보낼 수 있다니 경사스러운 일이로다!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:43.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,Being able to send Saigo, Kojirō, and Senhime along with them to the other world is truly a joyous occasion!
Comment: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.55,Default,ja,0,0,0,,さあ、こいつらを閉まり上げろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.55,Default,ko,0,0,0,,자, 저 놈들을 포박해라!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.55,Default,en,0,0,0,,Go get them!
Comment: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:54.49,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ど、どうしたんだ、いったい？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:54.49,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐, 뭔 일이냐, 대체?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:54.49,Default,en,0,0,0,,W- what's going on?!
Comment: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:58.37,Default,ja,0,0,0,,武蔵の兄ちゃん、助けに来たぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:58.37,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시 형, 구하러 왔어!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:58.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi bro, we're here to save you!
Comment: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:00.34,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ああ、ありがとうだす！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:00.34,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오, 고맙소!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:00.34,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thank you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:05.14,Default,ja,0,0,0,,武蔵殿、もうひと暴れしますか！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:05.14,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시 님, 다시 한번 날뛰어 봅시다!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:05.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,Mr. Musashi, why not rage around again?
Comment: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.26,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そうダス！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.26,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그렇소!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.26,Default,en,0,0,0,,You're right!
Comment: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:09.39,Default,ja,0,0,0,,サイゴーさん、この好きに不知火をやっつけるのよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:09.39,Default,ko,0,0,0,,사이고 씨, 이 틈에 시라누이를 처리해!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:09.39,Default,en,0,0,0,,Mr. Saigo, deal with those Shiranuis using this chance!
Comment: 0,0:16:09.81,0:16:10.86,Default,ja,0,0,0,,わかりました！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.81,0:16:10.86,Default,ko,0,0,0,,알겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.81,0:16:10.86,Default,en,0,0,0,,Understood!
Comment: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:14.90,Default,ja,0,0,0,,みんな、元気だな。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:14.90,Default,ko,0,0,0,,다들 활기차구나...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:14.90,Default,en,0,0,0,,Everyone's so energetic...
Comment: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:21.23,Default,ja,0,0,0,,チェスト！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:21.23,Default,ko,0,0,0,,체스트!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:21.23,Default,en,0,0,0,,Chest!
Comment: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:29.97,Default,ja,0,0,0,,兄ちゃん、刀持ってきたやったぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:29.97,Default,ko,0,0,0,,형, 칼 가져왔어!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:29.97,Default,en,0,0,0,,Bro, we took your swords!
Comment: 0,0:16:31.31,0:16:32.36,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ありがとうだす！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.31,0:16:32.36,Default,ko,0,0,0,,고맙소!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.31,0:16:32.36,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thank you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:33.96,Default,ja,0,0,0,,一朗太！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:33.96,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이치로타!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:33.96,Default,en,0,0,0,,Ichirota!
Comment: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:36.33,Default,ja,0,0,0,,父ちゃん！母ちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:36.33,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아빠! 엄마!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:36.33,Default,en,0,0,0,,Dad! Mom!
Comment: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:37.51,Default,ja,0,0,0,,一朗太！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:37.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이치로타!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:37.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,Ichirota!
Comment: 0,0:16:38.87,0:16:40.91,Default,ja,0,0,0,,会いたかったよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.87,0:16:40.91,Default,ko,0,0,0,,보고 싶었어!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.87,0:16:40.91,Default,en,0,0,0,,I wanted to see you!
Comment: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:41.86,Default,ja,0,0,0,,みんな無事か。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:41.86,Default,ko,0,0,0,,다들 괜찮구나.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:41.86,Default,en,0,0,0,,Are everyone alright?
Comment: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:46.11,Default,ja,0,0,0,,一朗太のお父さんだすか！よかっただす！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:46.11,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이치로타의 아버지이오! 잘 됐소!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:46.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,You must be Ichirota's father-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! What a relief-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:52.15,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ところで、伝説の秘剣、鳳凰丸は無事だすか、それとも鉄くずにされてしまっただすか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:52.15,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그나저나, 전설의 비검 봉황환은 괜찮소, 아니면 쇠 부스러기가 되어 버렸소?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:52.15,Default,en,0,0,0,,By the way, is that legendary secret sword Hououmaru alright-{\i1}dasu{\i0}, or did it become scrap iron-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:54.36,Default,ja,0,0,0,,鳳凰丸だけは隠してあります。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:54.36,Default,ko,0,0,0,,봉황환만은 숨겨 두었습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:54.36,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hououmaru is hidden and safe.
Comment: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:57.93,Default,ja,0,0,0,,よかっただす！ぜひ、コジローに譲ってほしいダス！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:57.93,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잘 됐소! 꼭 코지로에게 양도해 주시면 좋겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:57.93,Default,en,0,0,0,,Great to know-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I'd like you to give that to Kojirō-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:16:58.36,0:17:02.49,Default,ja,0,0,0,,もし、コジロー殿に持つふさわしい能力があれば構わないんですが。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.36,0:17:02.49,Default,ko,0,0,0,,만약 코지로 님에게 가질 자격이 될 능력이 있다면 괜찮습니다만...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.36,0:17:02.49,Default,en,0,0,0,,If Mr. Kojirō has a qualifying capacity to have one, then I can...
Comment: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:04.79,Default,ja,0,0,0,,え？その能力とはなんだす？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:04.79,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어? 그 능력이 뭣이오?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:04.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh? What is that capacity-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:12.74,Default,ja,0,0,0,,今までにも何人ごの武芸者が鳳凰丸を求めにまいりましたが、誰一人さやから抜くことができなかった出す。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:12.74,Default,ko,0,0,0,,지금까지 수많은 무예가가 봉황환을 보고 오셨지만, 지금까지 그 누구 하나 빼내지 못했습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:12.74,Default,en,0,0,0,,Until now, numerous martial artists came, looking for Hououmaru, but nobody has ever managed to take it out.
Comment: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:15.26,Default,ja,0,0,0,,刀が抜けないんだすか。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:15.26,Default,ko,0,0,0,,칼이 안 빠지오?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:15.26,Default,en,0,0,0,,The sword's stuck-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:18.33,Default,ja,0,0,0,,もし、コジローが抜けたら大丈夫ダスか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:18.33,Default,ko,0,0,0,,만약 코지로가 뺄 수 있으면 괜찮소?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:18.33,Default,en,0,0,0,,If Kojirō can pull it out, can he have it-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:19.86,Default,ja,0,0,0,,それもありますが。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:19.86,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그럴 수도 있겠지만...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:19.86,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's possible...
Comment: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:27.11,Default,ja,0,0,0,,不知火が火を払ったでゴワス。みんな逃げろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:27.11,Default,ko,0,0,0,,시라누이가 불을 지폈소. 다들 달아나쇼!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:27.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,Shiranui has set up a fire-{\i1}gowasu{\i0}. Everyone, escape!
Comment: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:31.71,Default,ja,0,0,0,,コジロー！早く！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:31.71,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코지로! 어서!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:31.71,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojirō! Hurry!
Comment: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:46.27,Default,ja,0,0,0,,助かったダス。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:46.27,Default,ko,0,0,0,,살았소...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:46.27,Default,en,0,0,0,,We live-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:48.95,Default,ja,0,0,0,,安心してるのはまだ早いぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:48.95,Default,ko,0,0,0,,안심하긴 이르다!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:48.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's too early to relive!
Comment: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:03.40,Default,ja,0,0,0,,皆殺しにしてくれるわ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:03.40,Default,ko,0,0,0,,몰살시켜 주겠다!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:03.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,You'll all be annihilated!
Comment: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.16,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ああ、疲れた。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.16,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 지쳤다.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.16,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'm tired.
Comment: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:11.21,Default,ja,0,0,0,,コジローったら。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:11.21,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코지로도 참...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:11.21,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojirō...
Comment: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.03,Default,ja,0,0,0,,鳳凰丸はどこだすか！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.03,Default,ko,0,0,0,,봉황환은 어디 있소!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.03,Default,en,0,0,0,,Where is Hououmaru-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!
Comment: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:15.67,Default,ja,0,0,0,,隠してありますから、今とってきます！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:15.67,Default,ko,0,0,0,,숨겨 두었으니까 지금 가져 오겠습니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:15.67,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's hidden for now; I'll go take it!
Comment: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:16.97,Default,ja,0,0,0,,お願いするダス！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:16.97,Default,ko,0,0,0,,부탁드리오!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:16.97,Default,en,0,0,0,,Please do so-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:45.20,Default,ja,0,0,0,,チェスト！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:45.20,Default,ko,0,0,0,,체스트!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:45.20,Default,en,0,0,0,,Chest!
Comment: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:55.85,Default,ja,0,0,0,,必殺！へぞ切り！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:55.85,Default,ko,0,0,0,,필살! 가랑이 차기!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:55.85,Default,en,0,0,0,,Special move! Crotch Kick!
Comment: 0,0:18:56.92,0:18:57.69,Default,ja,0,0,0,,痛い？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.92,0:18:57.69,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아파?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.92,0:18:57.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,Did that hurt?
Comment: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:01.83,Default,ja,0,0,0,,手ごわいやつら！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:01.83,Default,ko,0,0,0,,만만찮은 놈들이군!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:01.83,Default,en,0,0,0,,Pretty tough, eh?!
Comment: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:10.82,Default,ja,0,0,0,,不知火妖術、イカヅチ弾！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:10.82,Default,ko,0,0,0,,시라누이 요술 이카즈치 탄!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:10.82,Default,en,0,0,0,,Shiranui Magic, Ikazuchi Shell!
Comment: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:15.98,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ジュウベエさん！サイゴーさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:15.98,Default,ko,0,0,0,,쥬베 씨! 사이고 씨!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:15.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,Mr. Jube! Mr. Saigo!
Comment: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:23.82,Default,ja,0,0,0,,武蔵さん！鳳凰丸を持ってきました！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:23.82,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시 씨! 봉황환을 가져왔습니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:23.82,Default,en,0,0,0,,Mr. Musashi! I took Hououmaru!
Comment: 0,0:19:26.19,0:19:27.24,Default,ja,0,0,0,,危ないダス！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.19,0:19:27.24,Default,ko,0,0,0,,조심하시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.19,0:19:27.24,Default,en,0,0,0,,Watch out-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:46.15,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いつものびびしいコジローに戻ったわ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:46.15,Default,ko,0,0,0,,원래의 화려하고 아름다운 코지로로 돌아왔어!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:46.15,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojirō's back to his original beautiful look!
Comment: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:53.94,Default,ja,0,0,0,,鳳凰丸が抜けたダス！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:53.94,Default,ko,0,0,0,,봉황환이 빠졌소!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:53.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,He pulled out Hououmaru-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:19:58.14,0:20:00.70,Default,ja,0,0,0,,不知火妖術、イカヅチ弾！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.14,0:20:00.70,Default,ko,0,0,0,,시라누이 요술 이카즈치 탄!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.14,0:20:00.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,Shiranui Magic, Ikazuchi Shell!
Comment: 0,0:20:03.25,0:20:04.70,Default,ja,0,0,0,,コジロー！危ないダス！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.25,0:20:04.70,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코지로! 위험하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.25,0:20:04.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojirō! Watch out-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:10.32,Default,ja,0,0,0,,な、なんとしたのだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:10.32,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐, 뭔 짓이냐!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:10.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,W- what are you doing?!
Comment: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:57.39,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あ、気が付いたわ！コジロー、大丈夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:57.39,Default,ko,0,0,0,,정신 차렸어! 코지로, 괜찮아?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:57.39,Default,en,0,0,0,,He woke up! Kojirō, are you alright?
Comment: 0,0:20:57.85,0:20:58.80,Default,ja,0,0,0,,よかっただす！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:20:58.80,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잘 됐소!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:20:58.80,Default,en,0,0,0,,What a relief-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:01.76,Default,ja,0,0,0,,わ、私は一体。。。どうして。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:01.76,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나, 난 대체... 어째서...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:01.76,Default,en,0,0,0,,W- what... was I doing?
Comment: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:05.48,Default,ja,0,0,0,,何時間も気を失っていたのよ。心配しちゃった。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:05.48,Default,ko,0,0,0,,몇 시간이고 정신을 잃어서 걱정했어.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:05.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,You were unconscious for numerous hours. We were so worried!
Comment: 0,0:21:05.96,0:21:16.66,Default,ja,0,0,0,,鳳凰丸を抜くことが出来、しかも、その剣から黄金の鳥を出現させたものあらば、そのものに鳳凰丸をあたいよと、天草島に言い伝えがあります。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.96,0:21:16.66,Default,ko,0,0,0,,봉황환을 뺄 수 있었던 데다가 그 검에서 황금의 새를 출현시킨 자라면, 그 자에게 봉황환을 넘기라고 아마쿠사 섬에 구전되어 내려옵니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.96,0:21:12.24,Default,en,0,0,0,,The legends of Amakusa Island say that the one to pull out Hououmaru and
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.24,0:21:16.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,make the Golden Bird appear will take Hououmaru.
Comment: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:21.40,Default,ja,0,0,0,,だから、コジローさん、あなたに改めて鳳凰丸を差し上げましょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:21.40,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그러니까 코지로 씨, 당신에게 이 봉황환을 드리겠습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:21.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,So, Mr. Kojirō, you can have this Hououmaru.
Comment: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:24.86,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ありがたき幸せ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:24.86,Default,ko,0,0,0,,정말 감사합니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:24.86,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Comment: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:30.48,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ただし、黄金の鳥が現れたときは、全精力を使い果たす覚悟。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:30.48,Default,ko,0,0,0,,다만 황금의 새가 나타난 때에는 정신력을 다 소모할 각오를.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:30.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,But when the Golden Bird appears, be prepared to exhaust your mental powers.
Comment: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:39.30,Default,ja,0,0,0,,わかりました。このコジロー、世のため、人のため、ひいては千姫のために、この鳳凰丸に役立たずって見せましょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:39.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,알겠습니다. 이 코지로, 세상을 위해, 사람을 위해, 나아가서는 센히메를 위해, 이 봉황환에 걸맞는 모습을 보여드리겠습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:39.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,Understood. I, Kojirō, will live up to Hououmaru, not only for the world and for the people, but also for Senhime.
Comment: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:42.51,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あら、まだ気障に決めちゃって。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:42.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어라, 또 잘난 척 시작했소.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:42.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey, he began acting cool again-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:21:43.27,0:21:46.28,Default,ja,0,0,0,,でも、そのほうが落ち込んでるコジローよりいいダスな。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.27,0:21:46.28,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그래도 그 쪽이 침울한 코지로보다는 낫소!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.27,0:21:46.28,Default,en,0,0,0,,But that's still better than depressed Kojirō-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:50.72,Default,ja,0,0,0,,本当。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:50.72,Default,ko,0,0,0,,정말.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:50.72,Default,en,0,0,0,,Agreed!
Comment: 0,0:21:57.40,0:22:01.92,NoteOnAnimeVert,ja,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\fad(1800,0)\move(225,223,-80,223,2276,4520)}物干竿の墓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.40,0:22:01.92,NoteOnAnimeVert,ko,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\alphaFF\t(0,1800,2.5,\alpha00\3a20)\move(205,223,-100,223,2276,4520)\fs40\3c&H8DA2AB&\c&H000000&\bord8}모노호시자오의\N무덤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.40,0:22:01.92,NoteOnAnimeVert,en,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\alphaFF\t(0,1800,2.5,\alpha00\3a20)\move(225,223,-80,223,2276,4520)\fs32\3c&H8DA2AB&\c&H000000&\bord8}Tomb of Monohoshizao
Comment: 0,0:22:00.55,0:22:09.46,Default,ja,0,0,0,,わが半生を共にした愛刀、物干竿よ、お前があったからこそ私が鳳凰丸を手にすることが出来たのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.55,0:22:09.46,Default,ko,0,0,0,,{\i1}내 반생을 함께한 애도 모노호시자오여. 네가 있어서 이 내가 봉황환을 손에 넣을 수 있었다.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.55,0:22:09.46,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dear my beloved sword Monohoshizao. I could claim Hououmaru only because you were with me for the half of my life.
Comment: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:11.71,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ここで安らかに眠れ。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:11.71,Default,ko,0,0,0,,{\i1}여기서 편히 쉬어라.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:11.71,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rest in peace.
Comment: 0,0:22:13.57,0:22:17.91,Default,ja,0,0,0,,武蔵達が再び不知火一族の本拠を求めて、ふらべした。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.57,0:22:17.91,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시 일행은 다시 시라누이 일족의 본거를 향해 떠났다.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.57,0:22:17.91,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi and others have again departed to the base of Shiranui Clan.
Comment: 0,0:22:18.36,0:22:23.65,Default,ja,0,0,0,,だが、行く手に待っているのは花か、嵐か、大噴火か！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.36,0:22:23.65,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그렇지만 그들 앞에 기다리는 것은 꽃인가, 폭풍인가, 대분화인가!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.36,0:22:23.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,But what will be waiting in front of them: flowers, storms, or a violent eruption?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.17,0:22:44.21,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,허공의 주머니에 달이
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.17,0:22:44.21,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Sometimes the moon jumps over
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.93,0:22:47.47,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,뛰어넘어가는 일도 있어
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.93,0:22:47.47,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,the pocket of empty sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:49.85,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,큰 소리로 웃으면
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:49.85,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Laugh loudly and
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:52.48,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,내일에는 아침이 와
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:52.48,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,morning will come tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.23,0:22:57.81,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,잃는 것 따위는 아무것도 아니야
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.23,0:22:57.81,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Don't worry too much about losing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.81,0:23:01.40,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,계속 해나가! 앞으로 가!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.81,0:23:01.40,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Keep going! Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.40,0:23:03.82,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,맨손은 강해
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.40,0:23:03.82,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,A bare hand is strong
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.24,0:23:13.91,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,그런 거야! 가볍게 가자
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.24,0:23:13.91,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how it is! Let's go lightly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:21.96,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,인생 그런 거야! 기회가 어라,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:21.96,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how life is! Look, a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.42,0:23:26.68,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,꼬리를 흔들며 쫒아와!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.42,0:23:26.68,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,follows us wagging its tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:37.60,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,그런 거야! 가볍게 가자
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:37.60,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how it is! Let's go lightly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:46.07,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,미래도 그런 거야! 내일이 어라,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:46.07,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how the future is, too! Look, tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.32,0:23:51.91,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,양손을 벌리고 웃고 있어!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.32,0:23:51.91,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,is opening its hands and smiling at us!
Comment: 0,0:24:05.41,0:24:07.91,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おせんちゃんたら、本当に心配女だすな。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.41,0:24:07.91,Default,ko,0,0,0,,센짱도 참, 걱정 많이 하는 여자이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.41,0:24:07.91,Default,en,0,0,0,,Sen-chan sure worries a lot-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:24:08.17,0:24:11.22,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいら、ヒーローだからそう簡単にはやられないだすよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.17,0:24:11.22,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나는 히로니까 그렇게 간단히는 안 당하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.17,0:24:11.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'm a hero, and I don't get taken down that easily-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:24:11.22,0:24:17.29,Default,ja,0,0,0,,っと思ったんだけど、一人不知火一族の本拠地を目指したおいらの前に、恐るべき敵、げんば！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.22,0:24:17.29,Default,ko,0,0,0,,라고 생각했는데 혼자 시라누이 일족의 본거지를 찾고 있던 내 앞에 무서운 겐바가!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.22,0:24:17.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's what I thought, but Genba has appeared in front of me during I was looking for Shiranui Clan's headquarters!
Comment: 0,0:24:17.78,0:24:21.00,Default,ja,0,0,0,,溶岩弾にやられたおいらは火山の中にまっさがさら！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.78,0:24:21.00,Default,ko,0,0,0,,용암탄에 당한 나는 화산 안으로 풍덩!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.78,0:24:21.00,Default,en,0,0,0,,I got hit by lava shell, and into a volcano, {\i1}splash{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:24:21.55,0:24:24.44,Default,ja,0,0,0,,次回、アリ？武蔵は死んだダス
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.55,0:24:24.44,Default,ko,0,0,0,,다음 이야기! 어라? 무사시는 죽소
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.55,0:24:24.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,Next story! What?! Musashi Dies
Comment: 0,0:24:24.71,0:24:27.42,Default,ja,0,0,0,,疾風怒濤の地獄谷ダス！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.71,0:24:27.42,Default,ko,0,0,0,,질풍노도의 지옥곡이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.71,0:24:27.42,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's a stormy hell valley!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.86,0:24:30.86,NoteOnAnime,ko,60,0,60,,{\an7}다음 이야기
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.86,0:24:30.86,TitleEP,ko,0,0,225,,어라?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.86,0:24:30.86,TitleEP,ko,0,0,110,,무사시는 죽소
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.86,0:24:30.86,NoteOnAnime,ko,0,60,30,,{\an3\fs32}재미있게 보세요!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.86,0:24:30.86,NoteOnAnime,en,60,0,60,,{\an7}Next Story
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.86,0:24:30.86,TitleEP,en,0,0,225,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.86,0:24:30.86,TitleEP,en,0,0,110,,Musashi Dies
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.86,0:24:30.86,NoteOnAnime,en,0,60,30,,{\an3\fs32}We hope you enjoy!
